### Add a user to the waiting list
POST http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### Add another user to the waiting list
POST http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "Jane",
  "lastname": "Smith",
  "email": "jane.smith@example.com"
}

### Add a user with duplicate email (expect 409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@example.com"
}

### Add a user with missing firstname (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "missing@example.com"
}

### Add a user with missing lastname (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "",
  "email": "missing@example.com"
}

### Add a user with missing email (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": ""
}

### Add a user with invalid email (expect 400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstname": "John",
  "lastname": "Doe",
  "email": "not-an-email"
}

### Get all waiting list entries
GET http://localhost:8080/waitinglist
